# Project setup: #

Clone [bhammond:webix](https://github.com/bartonhammond/webix-account)
package as it is referenced.  You will have to setup for local development
(e.g. create a ./packages and from the packages/ directory do `ln -s /path/to/bhammond-webix/ webix`)

Then `meteor`

Demo: [webix-account-boilerplate](http://webix-account-boilerplate.meteor.com)


